    "body": "Hey guys. I am working on a plugin to manipulate time in tests and might have encountered the same issue, would love to send a PR but I would like to make sure the behaviour you are expecting is the same as I do.\r\n\r\n\r\nIMO the correct behaviour for this should be that increaseTime sets the difference in the timestamp between the latest block and the next one.\r\n\r\nThis, for example results in the fact that if you call increaseTime multiple times before mining, only the last one matters, which might be undesirable, so I am a liitle bit dubious. BTW, I think ganache's description implies a different thing from what I am saying.\r\n\r\nWhat do you think? @fvictorio ",
